"SLURM (Simple Linux Utility for Resource Management)",
"MPI (Message Passing Interface)",

"Tensorflow (optional)"

"NFS (Network File System)",
"HDFS (Hadoop Distributed File System)",
"HBase (Hadoop Database)",
"Spark (optional)"
],
"configuration": [
"MAGPIE_SCRIPTS_HOME",
"MAGPIE_LOCAL_DIR",
"MAGPIE_JOB_TYPE",

"MAGPIE_PYTHON",
"MPIRUN_OPTIONS"
]
}
}
